title: 'Remove Duplicates from List' - Easy
description:
Write a function `remove_duplicates` that takes a list of elements as input and returns the same list without any duplicate elements.

#### Function Signature
```python
def remove_duplicates(lst: List[Any]) -> List[Any]:
``` 

#### Input
- `lst` (List[Any]): A list of any data type that may contain duplicate elements.

#### Output
- Returns a list containing the same elements as input but without any duplicates.
